{"tid":305862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港男係筍盤？】ViuTV駱振偉丹麥女友：港男細心幽默照顧周到","createTime":"2017-07-02T05:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T06:01:38.000Z","uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c863b07888a01b06da5c3f980bedbc9d68911e","tid":305862,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170702/56897523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170702%2F56897523&d=3kuNeJD51JJbiD%2FxdPUtNDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e3d2d785\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170702%2F56897523&h=b982d8a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170702/56897523</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近年不時有人將港男與其他國家男士比較，說港男這樣不好，那樣不行，記者在街頭訪問了幾位香港女士，大致指港男有以下幾個缺點──無主見、唔成熟、吊兒郎當、無自信、思想幼稚、解決問題時一直逃避&hellip;&hellip;但另一邊廂，與ViuTV藝人駱振偉（Thor）拍拖三年多、來自丹麥的女生Katrine，卻對港男評價很高：「丹麥男生覺得女性應懂得照顧自己，無咁sweet，雖然會給予對方自由，但比較沒有風度，反而香港男仔好細心，細微位都照顧得很周到，還有很多有趣想法，很幽默。」到底港男做過甚麼會令Katrine有這感覺？Thor又會怎樣回應坊間對港男的指控？請睇片"},{"pid":"aa0aa340ad43456565a955b57b91eb0ff33e1071","tid":305862,"uid":48295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"Thor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e7bbc66dd79549b188b74f7540d919bd8b685b","tid":305862,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}